@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
actor Admin
participant "Admin UI" as UI
participant "User Manager" as UserMgmt
participant "Config Manager" as Config
participant "Audit Logger" as Logger
database "User DB" as DB

Admin -> UI : Login (Admin Credentials)
UI -> Auth : Authenticate
Auth --> UI : Success (Role: Admin)

Admin -> UI : Create New User (Role: Nurse)
UI -> UserMgmt : Validate & Create
UserMgmt -> DB : Store User Data
UserMgmt -> Logger : Log: "Admin created new user: [NurseID]"
UI --> Admin : User Created Successfully

== Security & System Audit ==
Admin -> UI : View Global Audit Trail [S-D-02]
UI -> Logger : Request All Immutable Logs
Logger -> Logger : Verify Integrity (No Deletions)
Logger --> UI : Return Full System History
UI --> Admin : Display Logs (Read-Only)

Admin -> UI : Update System Config (Simulation Speed)
UI -> Config : Set Simulation Parameters
Config -> Logger : Log: "Global Config Updated"
UI --> Admin : Settings Saved
@enduml